General.Name: XMReality AB
General.Description: XMReality AB (publ) develops and sells solutions for knowledge transfer through augmented reality (AR) globally. The company offers XMReality Remote Guidance, a visual support tool that is used to guide onsite staff through AR to solve problems or prevent them from occurring. It also provides AR smart glasses. The company serves manufacturing, energy and utilities, housing and real estate, food and beverage, and packaging industries. XMReality AB (publ) was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Linköping, Sweden.
